This tells cron:

    â€œRun this script every 2 minutes.â€

âœ… You can change */2 to:

    */1 â†’ every minute

    */5 â†’ every 5 minutes

ğŸ”¹ 3. Save and exit

In nano:

    Press Ctrl + O to save

    Press Enter

    Press Ctrl + X to exit

ğŸ” Optional: Add logging

To keep a log of every cron-triggered run:

